t","label":"Cron: 空闲检测自主学习","displayName":"webchat:g-agent-main-cron-3709e1d2-67b1-4eff-92e4-b586ec802978","deliveryContext":{"channel":"webchat"},"updatedAt":1774666129882,"sessionId":"71c99898-ac60-41bd-850a-fd97af9ae968","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":44791,"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"webchat","transcriptPath":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/agents/main/sessions/71c99898-ac60-41bd-850a-fd97af9ae968.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me check for active sessions first before executing the autonomous learning task."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_qr3ruryubmj1_1","name":"sessions_list","arguments":{"activeMinutes":5,"messageLimit":1}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774666130662}]}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774666135081}}
{"type":"message","id":"9aaea6a7","parentId":"4d5fd7ab","timestamp":"2026-03-28T02:48:59.217Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The only session in the last 5 minutes is the cron session itself. This cron job is the one running right now, triggered by itself. There are no other user conversations. I should execute the autonomous learning task.\n\nLet me search for latest news on enterprise digital transformation, smart security, network system integration, and IT operations services.","thinkingSignature":"e34dcb533b7ed0d1666533e74f80f14b64c89e2a55a53170ba11ae15a823b784"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_c45w28l6apns_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":811,"output":111,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44903,"cost":{"input":0.00024329999999999998,"output":0.00013319999999999999,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00169593}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774666135084}}
{"type":"message","id":"04823c25","parentId":"9aaea6a7","timestamp":"2026-03-28T02:48:59.223Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_c45w28l6apns_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774666139220}}
{"type":"message","id":"7e637eb0","parentId":"04823c25","timestamp":"2026-03-28T02:49:05.199Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me search for the latest information on enterprise digital transformation, smart security, network system integration, and IT operations services in China.","thinkingSignature":"2088b36359de0309c7d1e116f0fdad5b47b1abd3d22ba8e994ee62e3ca69890e"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ry9cuue23y94_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型 2026最新动态 政策\" --output json 2>/dev/null | head -200"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ry9cuue23y94_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"智能安防 行业发展趋势 2026\" --output json 2>/dev/null | head -200"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ry9cuue23y94_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"网络系统集成 IT运维服务 行业动态 2026\" --output json 2>/dev/null | head -200"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1437,"output":187,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45605,"cost":{"input":0.00043109999999999996,"output":0.00022439999999999998,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0019749299999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774666139223}}
